UI Specifications

1. Layout
	‚Ä¢	Two-column layout
	‚Ä¢	Left: Filters, search, and tabs.
	‚Ä¢	Right: Notification list.
	‚Ä¢	Spacing & Alignment
	‚Ä¢	Use 8px and 16px spacing for consistency.
	‚Ä¢	Notifications should have a clear hierarchy (title, description, timestamp).
	‚Ä¢	Card-Based UI
	‚Ä¢	Each notification should be in a card format for clear separation.
	‚Ä¢	Unread notifications should have a light background highlight.

2. Components

